Class ElektronineKnyga

java.lang.Object
biblioteka.core.Leidinys
biblioteka.core.Knyga
biblioteka.core.ElektronineKnyga
All Implemented Interfaces:
Borrowable, Digital, Downloadable, Postponable, Serializable, Cloneable
public class ElektronineKnyga extends Knyga implements Downloadable
Represents an electronic book (e-book) in the library. This class extends Knyga and implements the Downloadable interface, providing details specific to digital formats, such as file format, size in MB, and a download counter. E-books typically cannot be borrowed in the traditional sense.
